{"tid":1806083,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 國際戰缐 ] 歐洲巡迴展覧團隊眾籌 只係要多十零萬 一人捐少少搞掂佢啦","createTime":"2020-01-01T05:12:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T05:13:32.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"28c3174679373f4691cd78ba6ee4f5dabcb231b2","tid":1806083,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:12:04.000Z","msg":"<ins></ins>眾籌網址 :<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/free-hong-kong-europe-touring-exhibition/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Ffree-hong-kong-europe-touring-exhibition%2F&d=EyvET%2B%2BaCRTqAKFB3QLIc5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=1a0525e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/free-hong-kong-europe-touring-exhibition/</a><br />\n<br />\n各位手足，我哋係Free Hong Kong Exhibition團隊，由一班海外香港人組成，主要打國際戰線。我哋希望以巡迴展覧嘅形式，將香港人嘅聲音帶到海外。作為响城牆外面生活嘅人，我哋自覺有責任將港共政府嘅所作所為話俾全世界知。响西方民主社會，人民就係力量，政府嘅決策同立法往往都以民意為依歸，而展覽正正可以提供一個空間同平台，直接同市民接觸交流。我哋希望以普羅大眾為出發點，提高民間對香港事態嘅關注，團結國際民運陣線，希望响國際間有更加多迴響，間接向港共政府施壓。<br />\n<br />\n由九月開始，我哋已經先後响德國三個城市自資舉辦咗三次展覽同一次講座，亦協辦咗一個sharing session，近期亦同其他歐洲城市聯絡緊，希望將展覽帶到更多地方，遍地開花，與更多外國人接觸，團結國際力量。經過三次展覽之後，我們團隊經已山窮水盡，所以希望透過眾籌籌集經費，繼續 [和你展]。下一階段我們打算到比利時、丹麥，我哋亦已同烏克蘭當地聯絡，希望响寒冬凜烈嘅十二月或一月直達基輔，同五年前烏克蘭革命人民接觸，連結國際民運陣線。<br />\n<br />\n我哋今次眾籌目標係三萬歐元，折合大約為港幣二十六萬五千元，用作未來幾個月再舉辦展覧同講座嘅開支。巡迴展覧結束之後如有任何剩餘資金，將會全數捐贈星火同盟。<br />\n<br />\n希望各位手足可以幫忙，課一課金，亦可以幫忙share，感謝大家。<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n我哋團隊facebook page :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Free-Hong-Kong-Exhibition-110062053719239/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFree-Hong-Kong-Exhibition-110062053719239%2F&d=EyvET%2B%2BaCRTqAKFB3QLIc5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=79db22a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Free-Hong-Kong-Exhibition-110062053719239/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wxVhzFS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwxVhzFS.jpg&h=94f011dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ZVmgTJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ZVmgTJ.jpg&h=a5c03ad3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qo5EN0q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQo5EN0q.jpg&h=2314032e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6J1XzFs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6J1XzFs.jpg&h=a2b5f3f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時事台轉載"},{"pid":"ed63d78b91875c9a3873f5889453feb667787d2a","tid":1806083,"uid":171313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:12:41.000Z","msg":"捐咗"},{"pid":"e9895237a446ff7baa7438840d705f5804924ce8","tid":1806083,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:21:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6130f78d5b179a5ecf979c2b48b9c0872c896a90","tid":1806083,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed63d78b91875c9a3873f5889453feb667787d2a","tid":1806083,"uid":171313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:12:41.000Z","msg":"捐咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T18:42:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80bf18c6f6fb745054aec0ce50b347de989c399","tid":1806083,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T18:44:25.000Z","msg":"Push lm"},{"pid":"afc59310fe6dbc4924007fdf72132178725ddca0","tid":1806083,"uid":35155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T18:48:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab50d5047e662267cf0dba16995b8a58ad2cbd0e","tid":1806083,"uid":151539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T18:48:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ad556caa916b9fafa7422897c0b471bd2d0b933","tid":1806083,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:53:19.000Z","m